author: Cipolla, Bartolomeo (1420-1475)
title: Cautele nove ultra Cepollam domini Thome Ferratii de advocatis de Brixia, j. u. peritissimi. - A la fin : Expliciunt cautele nove ultra Cepollam domini Thome Ferracij de advocatis de Brixia, j. u. peritissimi, cum consilio dominorum Signorelli de Homede
